fields.description:
Optionally emit a single JSON line that model can parse reliably:

SANDBOX_DIAGNOSTIC={
  "usingSandbox": true,
  "filesystemMode": "workspace-write",
  "networkMode": "deny",
  "networkAllowlist": null,
  "classification": { "kind": "network", "subtype": "dns", "evidence": "Could not resolve host", "confidence": "medium" }
}

This avoids model hallucinating why DNS failed.

DoD: JSON emission + system prompt hint about parsing SANDBOX_DIAGNOSTIC
